text: Anna Meysak (born 16 April 1984) is a Belarusian gymnast. She competed in four events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belarus Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Grodno
